{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 51}\uc1\u8220*Mighty are the deeds of his arm!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
2 He has scattered the self-satisfied proud,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
1{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 52}he has cast down the mighty from their thrones,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
2 and he uplifts the humble,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
1{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 53}he has filled the hungry with good things,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
