{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And the devil led Jesus up, and showing him in a single moment all the kingdoms of the earth, said to him,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}\uc1\u8220*I will give you all this power, and the splendor of them; for it has been given into my hands and I give it to whom I wish.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}If you worship me, it will all be yours.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}And Jesus answered him, \uc1\u8220*Scripture says \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8216*You should worship the Lord your God, and worship him only.\uc1\u8217*\uc1\u8221*
