{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 31}\uc1\u8220*To what then,\uc1\u8221* Jesus continued, \uc1\u8220*should I compare the people of the present generation? What are they like?{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 32}They are like some little children who are sitting in the marketplace and calling out to one another \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8216*We have played the flute for you, but you have not danced; We have wailed, but you have not wept!\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 33}For now that John the Baptist has come, not eating bread or drinking wine, you are saying \uc1\u8216*He has a demon in him\uc1\u8217*;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 34}and now that the Son of Man has come, eating and drinking, you are saying \uc1\u8216*Here is a glutton and a wine-drinker, a friend of tax collectors and outcasts.\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 35}And yet wisdom is vindicated by all her children.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

