 \uc1\u8220*Pray do so, teacher,\uc1\u8221* Simon answered; and Jesus began,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 41}\uc1\u8220*There were two people who were in debt to a moneylender; one owed five hundred silver coins, and the other fifty.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 42}As they were unable to pay, he forgave them both. Which of them, do you think, will love him the more?\uc1\u8221*
