{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
 \uc1\u8220*You are right,\uc1\u8221* said Jesus,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 44}and then, turning to the woman, he said to Simon, \uc1\u8220*Do you see this woman? I came into your house \uc1\u8211* you gave me no water for my feet, but she has made my feet wet with her tears and dried them with her hair.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 45}You did not give me one kiss, but she, from the moment I came in, has not ceased to kiss my feet.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 46}You did not anoint even my head with oil, but she has anointed my feet with perfume.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 47}So I tell you, her great love shows that her sins, many as they are, have been pardoned. One who is pardoned little loves little.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 48}Then he said to the woman, \uc1\u8220*Your sins have been pardoned.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 49}The other guests began to say to one another, \uc1\u8220*Who is this man who even pardons sins?\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 50}But Jesus said to the woman, \uc1\u8220*Your faith has delivered you; go, and peace be with you.\uc1\u8221*
