{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 50}\uc1\u8220*None of you must prevent him,\uc1\u8221* Jesus said to John, \uc1\u8220*whoever is not against you is for you.\uc1\u8221*
