{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 58}\uc1\u8220*Foxes have holes,\uc1\u8221* he replied, \uc1\u8220*and wild birds their nests, but the Son of Man has nowhere to lay his head.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 59}To another man Jesus said, \uc1\u8220*Follow me.\uc1\u8221*
