{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Give us each day the bread that we will need;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}and forgive us our sins,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 for we ourselves forgive everyone who wrongs us;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 and take us not into temptation.\uc1\u8217*\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard
