{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}\uc1\u8220*Why do you call me good?\uc1\u8221* answered Jesus. \uc1\u8220*No one is good but God.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}You know the commandments \uc1\u8211* Do not commit adultery, Do not kill, Do not steal, Do not say what is false about others, Honor your father and your mother.\uc1\u8221*
