{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}\uc1\u8220*I have observed all these,\uc1\u8221* he replied, \uc1\u8220*from childhood.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}Hearing this, Jesus said to him, \uc1\u8220*There is one thing still lacking in you; sell everything that you have, and distribute to the poor, and you will have wealth in heaven; then come and follow me.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}But the man became greatly distressed on hearing this, for he was extremely rich.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}Seeing this, Jesus said to his disciples, \uc1\u8220*How hard it is for the wealthy to enter the kingdom of God!{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}It is easier, indeed, for a camel to get through a needle\uc1\u8217*s eye than for a rich person to enter the kingdom of God!\uc1\u8221*
