 \uc1\u8220*Master,\uc1\u8221* he said, \uc1\u8220*I want to recover my sight.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 42}And Jesus said, \uc1\u8220*Recover your sight, your faith has delivered you.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 43}Instantly he recovered his sight, and began to follow Jesus, praising God. And all the people, on seeing it, gave glory to God.
